{"tid":1216852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本外相回應香港送中條例示威","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T13:24:25.000Z","uid":51271,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4aebb67ae8925a8b892ac1272e10b509870f47d6","tid":1216852,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:12:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/konotarogomame/status/1139024078138822656?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkonotarogomame%2Fstatus%2F1139024078138822656%3Fs%3D21&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=2e83cf18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkonotarogomame%2Fstatus%2F1139024078138822656%3Fs%3D21&h=3e7cea25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/konotarogomame/status/1139024078138822656?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n香港の友人として、最近の情勢を大変心配しています。特に多くの負傷者が出ていることに心を痛めています。平和的な話合いを通じて、事態が早期に収拾され、香港の自由と民主が維持されることを強く期待します。"},{"pid":"e6655c39e63cb648575127e53776e2dab3064870","tid":1216852,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:22:06.000Z","msg":"抵我拎晒Yen出黎支持"},{"pid":"7ba1f6091da06aefbbffb14208e062cfa612f85f","tid":1216852,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:25:51.000Z","msg":"唔識日文，有冇翻譯"},{"pid":"5758a1365b6234ddae6253177ebdb6f8bda6c6a3","tid":1216852,"uid":51271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"7ba1f6091da06aefbbffb14208e062cfa612f85f","tid":1216852,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:25:51.000Z","msg":"唔識日文，有冇翻譯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:26:40.000Z","msg":"As a friend of Hong Kong, I am very worried about the recent situation.  I am especially concerned that many injured people are out.  Through peaceful talks, I strongly hope that things will be settled early and Hong Kong's freedom and democracy will be maintained."},{"pid":"bd1e0820b1cccffe379c966b118279ea70a1e46f","tid":1216852,"uid":6435,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:27:44.000Z","msg":"【日本外務大臣河野太郎回應近日香港的狀況】<br />\n<br />\n河野大臣：「作為香港的朋友，最近的狀況讓我非常擔憂。特別是看到很多的受傷者，令我感到份外痛心。通過和平的討論，我強烈希望情況能早日穩定下來，得以維護香港的自由和民主。」"},{"pid":"48ec390a75ed99cd178eda4775a8bcec1f6cd3e5","tid":1216852,"uid":79563,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:30:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>請繼續鎖住郭紹傑，唔好比佢返香港！<br />\n<br />\nTHANKS!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"798d1a5ee705b603b23775287477e2a00879adec","tid":1216852,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48ec390a75ed99cd178eda4775a8bcec1f6cd3e5","tid":1216852,"uid":79563,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:30:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>請繼續鎖住郭紹傑，唔好比佢返香港！<br />\n<br />\nTHANKS!</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:30:57.000Z","msg":"Noted<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391b25a21452dd4bdd8a940a995dc56d2448f8fa","tid":1216852,"uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"bd1e0820b1cccffe379c966b118279ea70a1e46f","tid":1216852,"uid":6435,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:27:44.000Z","msg":"【日本外務大臣河野太郎回應近日香港的狀況】<br />\n<br />\n河野大臣：「作為香港的朋友，最近的狀況讓我非常擔憂。特別是看到很多的受傷者，令我感到份外痛心。通過和平的討論，我強烈希望情況能早日穩定下來，得以維護香港的自由和民主。」"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:31:25.000Z","msg":"(設計對白)<br />\n<br />\n河野大臣：「其實我地日本都係明治維新不斷暗殺幕府官員，再到最尾打贏幕府，先有民主自由。」"},{"pid":"d8533eea867674434671b76990dc9d7b9985b62f","tid":1216852,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"391b25a21452dd4bdd8a940a995dc56d2448f8fa","tid":1216852,"uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"bd1e0820b1cccffe379c966b118279ea70a1e46f","tid":1216852,"uid":6435,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedB